      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 16,
      "message": "this to_nice_yaml is potentially a problem, there are some bugreports opened for it that it doesnt produce output correctly. I tested this and in our case it's adding some empty rows into certificate ... not sure if this is functional impact as ConfigMap with cefrtificate looks correct,\n\nBut I would recommend adding: some task to remove empty rows \n\n# to_nice_yaml filter is wrongly adding empty lines\n- name: Remove blank lines from override_file\n  replace:\n    path: \"{{ app_helm_override_file }}\"\n    regexp: '(^\\n)'\n    replace: ''",
